item.title: Zombie Watch
item.description: Got to have a glimpse of what russian socio-patriotical channel “star” or “zvezda” shows on sunday mornings. first there was an episode about how many more people will have cancer in the future then they had one with staged excerpts related to people being executed by firing squads and how scout who was around this went into the mental house then they got to international politics and what prospects should be there for the state I do not do hatewatch normally.
